variable-sql.name: SQL_Multiple_Cases
variable-sql.query: select top 5000 acd.ACDetails_ID, acd.ACD_Pcn, acd.AuditCase_ID, acd.PatientVisitID as CasePatientVisitID from tblAMAuditCaseDetails(NOLOCK) acd join tblAMOverallStatus(NOLOCK) tao on tao.OS_ID = acd.ACD_OverallStatus_ID where acd.ACDetails_ID not in (select cp.ACDetails_ID from tblAMAuditCasePaymentOffsets(NOLOCK) cp) and acd.ACD_Pcn <> '' and tao.OS_Description not in ('Closed - Copy', 'Inactive') and acd.IsArchived = 0
